                "elements": [
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "I was not intending to be hostile. One should extend grace in one’s interpretations of off-the-cuff writing on the Internet.\n\nI took the time to look at your website — to search it, even, when I figured you had to give me some idea what this software is like to use. When I found none, I took the time to come back here and point this out. I was being a little tongue in cheek. I’m sorry that didn’t come across.\n\nI'm interested in what you’re doing — that’s why I took the time to go look at it. I’m still interested. But I’m certainly not going to sign up (apparently the only way to learn more right now) without some idea."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
